description:
Would it help you to check in every two weeks with people studying web development or working on side projects? Would you be interested in taking part in "Intro to.." workshops (on SQL or Git for example), or Python beginner workshops? Could you give a workshop yourself? If the answer to any of these questions is yes, please join this event.

CodeHub WebDev101 and mentoring sessions have been part of the fortnightly Workshop Wednesdays. This is to explore restarting them online.
title: CodeHub @ Workshop Wednesdays - Forum session
